  <description>Plants to 40 m. Winter buds pubescent, hairs relatively short, stiff. Leaves: blade base usually with 2 round basilaminar glands, apex long-acuminate, abaxial surface glabrous at emergence; preformed blade with (3–)7–15(–21) teeth on each side; neoformed blade lengths about equaling widths. Pedicels: lengths uniform, 1–6(–8 in fruit) mm. Capsules with thin, flexible valves.</description>
